public final class PersonName
extends com.google.api.client.json.GenericJson

Model definition for Plus.PersonName. An object representation of the individual components of a person's name. This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Plus service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need. For a detailed explanation, see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json
